title: Discover Mozambique, a gem of the old empire (VIDEO)
text:
Discover Mozambique, a gem of the old empire (VIDEO) Sunday October 11, 2015 Print Article 
MAPUTO, Oct 11 — Often overlooked despite being named a Unesco Heritage site in 1991, the Island of Mozambique is being given a second life by investors and tourists alike. — AFP-Relaxnews 
Screengrab of a video of the island of Mozambique. New life is being injected into this jewel of the old empire.
